These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, skydiving, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, basketball, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is baseball##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
3. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
4. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | hiking | skydiving | fishing  |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball   | surfing  | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, eggplant, apricot, peach
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, firefighter, social-worker, police-officer
1. the police-officer is not to the left of the police-officer##8
2. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
3. the person eating broccoli is the firefighter##1
4. the person eating peach is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating eggplant##2
5. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the coach##7
6. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
7. the coach is not to the left of the coach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | apricot | eggplant          | peach | broccoli     |
| Job    | social-worker      | police-officer | coach | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, software-developer, musician, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, scientific, zombie, disaster
1. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the musician##8
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
4. the software-developer is in an even position##4
5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
7. the writer is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | software-developer | musician     | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | disaster   | western | zombie    |

