.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, r&b, techno, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skiing, snowboarding, basketball
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
5. the fan of house is the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | r&b         | gospel   | house    |
| Sport         | skiing | basketball | snowboarding | rowing |

