.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, action, adventure, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, volleyball, golf
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching action movies##7
2. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching thriller movies##7
4. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is golf##8
5. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person who's sport is basketball##7
6. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
7. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | adventure | martial-arts | thriller    |
| Sport         | soccer | golf   | volleyball   | basketball |

