2. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
5. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
6. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
7. the person eating pomegranate is the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pomegranate | mango | grapes  | avocado |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | house         | electronic | techno |

