.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, juice, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, skateboarding, sailing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's sport is sailing##7
3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | juice | soy-milk | coffee   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | sailing | water-polo  | skateboarding |

