.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, punk, house, hip-hop
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, motorbike, helicopter, quad-bike
1. the fan of reggae is between the fan of hip-hop and the person driving the train##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the fan of house is not the person driving the helicopter##6
7. the fan of hip-hop is not to the right of the fan of house##8
8. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | reggae | house | punk |
| Transport     | quad-bike | motorbike       | train  | helicopter    |

