.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, mango, apricot, blueberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, writing, sudoku, photography
1. the person eating apricot is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person eating mango##8
3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating apricot is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
6. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
7. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | mango        | blueberry | apricot      | apple    |
| Hobby   | video-games | sudoku   | writing | photography |

