4. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking 7up##7
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
