.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, carrot, onion, pomegranate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, drama, comedy, western
 1. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
 3. the person eating potato is the person watching comedy movies##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
 5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating potato is not to the right of the person watching comedy movies##8
 9. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
10. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | carrot    | onion | potato | pomegranate |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  | comedy     | drama    |

