2. the person eating lemon is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating potato##1
6. the person eating potato is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person eating nectarine##2
