.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, pony, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, scooter, quad-bike
1. the owner of the bird is not the person driving the scooter##6
2. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the bird##7
4. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
5. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
6. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | ferret  | bird | guinea-pig  | pony  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | boat   | quad-bike | scooter |

