.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, dog, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bike, train
1. the person driving the boat is not the owner of the cat##6
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
4. the owner of the dog is the person driving the airplane##1
5. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person driving the airplane##7
6. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the train and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | goldfish    | goat | cat | dog |
| Transport   | boat | train      | bike     | airplane     |

 